# Clothing Store Management System

A clothing store management system that allows employees to manage the inventory and billing.

## Requirements

- Docker
- Node.js

## Getting Started

To run the clothing store management system as a Docker container, follow these steps:

1. Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/nicolas-media/clothing-store-managment.git

Copy code

2. Build the Docker image:

cd clothing-store-management
docker-compose build

Copy code

3. Run the Docker container:

docker-compose up

Copy code

4. Access the employee interface at http://localhost:3000.

